# .shellcheckrc - ShellCheck configuration for system-health-reporter
# https://github.com/koalaman/shellcheck/blob/master/shellcheck.1.md#rc-files

# Allow unused variables in demo/reporting scripts (common for placeholders)
# disable=SC2034

# Allow declaring+assigning in one line for simple readonly constants
# disable=SC2155

# Strict mode: only enable what we truly want to ignore
# (Recommended: fix warnings in code instead of suppressing globally)
